references: Related: CF 274619. Superseding: Ord 83834, Ord 85820, Ord 86878.
summary: AN ORDINANCE relating to the City's Health Care Program; authorizing execution of a new contract with National Health Assurance, Inc. to replace the contract with International Health and Life Insurance Company, authorizing certain modifications in the contracts with Group Health Cooperative of Puget Sound and King County Medical Blue Shield, and superseding Ordinances 83834, 85820 and 86878 to the extent inconsistent therewith.
